<ab>Wygeleis <expan>Schenk<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Geyren </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Schenk, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        habt, ewch von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs und des tags <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der bey uns sein sol,
                        etwas zu schreiben etc., also tun wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> haben, daz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der künig kürczlich dennoch auf dem Perg
                        gewest sey. So <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir auch noch niht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, denn daz der tag bey uns fürgank
                        gewinne und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die <expan>kurfurste<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und ander <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vast herberg bey uns
                                <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
